name: Journey's End
description: Part eight of our journey. We finally somewhat regain composure and make our way back home. Every journey must come to an end but I'm so grateful we got to travel together. We're greeted by a placard my mother made that makes us feel safe and welcomed. A piece of folk art made by Dawnia Darkstone's mother, photographed with Dawnia's circuitbent camera and digitally manipulated -@Letsglitchit
